<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accueil - FinSolutions</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 min-h-screen">
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
        
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-4">
                 FinSolutions
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
                Gérez vos finances personnelles en toute simplicité
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
                <a href="/login" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 transition shadow-lg text-lg">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt mr-2"></i>Se connecter
                </a>
                <a href="/register" class="bg-white text-purple-600 font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition shadow-lg text-lg border-2 border-purple-600">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-2"></i>S'inscrire
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition">
                <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-3xl text-green-600"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Suivi des transactions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Enregistrez et suivez toutes vos dépenses et revenus en temps réel</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition">
                <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-wallet text-3xl text-blue-600"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Gestion des budgets</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Définissez des budgets par catégorie et suivez vos objectifs</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition">
                <div class="bg-purple-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-pie text-3xl text-purple-600"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Statistiques détaillées</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Visualisez vos finances avec des graphiques et rapports</p>
            </div>
        </div>

      
        <div class="mt-16 text-center">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">100%</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Gratuit</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2"></p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Sécurisé</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2"></p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Responsive</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <footer class="text-center py-8 text-gray-600">
        <p>&copy; 2025 FinSolutions. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>